    <title>Proxy</title>
    <url>/2020/03/17/proxy/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本文在于介绍对npm以及git的代理设置<br>(ps:本文用的是vmess)</p>
<h2 id="对于NPM"><a href="#对于NPM" class="headerlink" title="对于NPM"></a>对于NPM</h2><h3 id="设置Proxy"><a href="#设置Proxy" class="headerlink" title="设置Proxy"></a>设置Proxy</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> proxy=http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> registry=http://registry.npmjs.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="关于https"><a href="#关于https" class="headerlink" title="关于https"></a>关于https</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> https-proxy http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="NPM代理用户名和密码"><a href="#NPM代理用户名和密码" class="headerlink" title="NPM代理用户名和密码"></a>NPM代理用户名和密码</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config <span class="built_in">set</span> proxy http://username:password@server:port</span><br><span class="line">npm confit <span class="built_in">set</span> https-proxy http://username:password@server:port</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="NPM取消代理"><a href="#NPM取消代理" class="headerlink" title="NPM取消代理"></a>NPM取消代理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config delete proxy</span><br><span class="line">npm config delete https-proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="NPM修改源"><a href="#NPM修改源" class="headerlink" title="NPM修改源"></a>NPM修改源</h3><p>More infor: <a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000002589144" target="_blank" rel="noopener">修改源</a></p>
<h2 id="对于-git"><a href="#对于-git" class="headerlink" title="对于 git"></a>对于 git</h2><h3 id="开启代理"><a href="#开启代理" class="headerlink" title="开启代理"></a>开启代理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:10809</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="取消代理"><a href="#取消代理" class="headerlink" title="取消代理"></a>取消代理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --<span class="built_in">unset</span> http.proxy </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git config --global --<span class="built_in">unset</span> https.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005LmDpBly1gd0qxm26mwj305k05k3yu.jpg" alt="cat.png"></p>
]]></content>
